{"tid":774263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港鐵指沉降數字是私隱　擔心影響當區樓價","createTime":"2018-08-10T07:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T09:05:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2ddc481e601b5a9a752b76e35a0f75394c0ab2","tid":774263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1735483/org/c4ffcae330b359f3872046cc3c38027b.jpg/Q8O3eEt-dO44a5Qi9lHZ1frwlLIkm1sKEHDp3hBw6d4?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1735483%2Forg%2Fc4ffcae330b359f3872046cc3c38027b.jpg%2FQ8O3eEt-dO44a5Qi9lHZ1frwlLIkm1sKEHDp3hBw6d4%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=c1228af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫土瓜灣站工程引致附近樓宇及煤氣喉管沉降事件，今早（10日）九龍城區議員何顯明在電台節目中表示，當區居民與區議員一直被蒙在鼓裡，港鐵從無公布沉降數字，更指「港鐵說沉降數字可能是私隱，若大廈有需要才給該座大廈看，稱<span style=\"color: red;\">擔心沉降數字會影響樓價</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n九龍城區議員林博就稱，昨煤氣公司致電區議員時，亦只能交代涉事7條喉管中4條的情況，並指煤氣一直無跟區議會匯報相關情況，是因為「未考慮到這麼嚴重」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/221034/%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8C%87%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%8D%80%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F221034%2F%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%2599%258D%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2593%259C%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1-%25E6%2593%2594%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9&d=HaxpEIr4Zh%2BcsyA%2BA%2FwXHBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fe46f515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/221034/%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%8C%87%E6%B2%89%E9%99%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1-%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%95%B6%E5%8D%80%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9</a>"},{"pid":"6f75000628cfd73e38a757c8acf0c2836f48813d","tid":774263,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"曲線救挫樓市"},{"pid":"a2621dd083828213237b8c197bcb54ef30e45a3b","tid":774263,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0718e119e006f8ee2def9b2f2d648a50409aebf","tid":774263,"uid":62650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"無人知但又咩都唔做!佢真係到死人個時點樣"},{"pid":"9003b7207fce859201d4916bd2a79330e6e91f56","tid":774263,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"係呀間屋漏水有蟻竇死過人係兇宅都係私穩，千其咪撚比買家知，呃尻佢就岩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你出左事咁多個月你都諗唔到個好少少的藉口，仆你個街"},{"pid":"9fb327f37ee1ec035d6a968c7728b9ea34c6216c","tid":774263,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0718e119e006f8ee2def9b2f2d648a50409aebf","tid":774263,"uid":62650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"無人知但又咩都唔做!佢真係到死人個時點樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"死咗都冇事 太陽從東邊昇起"},{"pid":"3ec4c7df488cf45b5762ac0902379843546395eb","tid":774263,"uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"公眾安全定私隱重要啲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班膠層個腦裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfa67b05111aa5c09c4a9f3e8148cb540e39b58","tid":774263,"uid":127788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"港鐵： 你死你事 我樓照起 關人撚事"},{"pid":"fcb5b4cb558e5ab168eaa8a8328153bb0761